massif-visualizer: massif-visualizer (valgrind massif visualizer)
massif-visualizer:
massif-visualizer: Massif Visualizer is a tool that - who'd guess that - visualizes
massif-visualizer: massif data. You run your application in Valgrind with --tool=massif
massif-visualizer: and then open the generated massif.out.%pid in the visualizer. Gzip
massif-visualizer: or Bzip2 compressed massif files can also be opened transparently.
massif-visualizer:
massif-visualizer: Homepage: https://apps.kde.org/massif_visualizer/
